{
  "stem": "942.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And how I managed to do this for a week or two, I really don't know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We took one, and then we went back for another one, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it just kept going, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that was another detail that I was working on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This is summer is gone, and the fall is coming.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And October of 1944.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You know, when the Allies landed in Normandy, we got sort of a bit of a, a hint of this.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I remember the guards were talking to each other.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And, you know, we were never able to see a newspaper.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But when the guards were reading the newspapers, and sometimes they either discarded a paper, and somebody picked it up, and they could read what was happening, so.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But you know, to me, Normandy was so far away, I couldn't even worry about it, you know.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Because I was right here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And you know, that was really of no concern, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "My lot did not get any better or whatever, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I remember in October, I was working on a farm.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This time we were working with potatoes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was, I think, middle of October.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And what we were doing, we were stacking potatoes in a big pit, storing it away for the winter.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a big farm.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were taking these potatoes on wheelbarrows.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was able to snatch a potato every now and then and just eat it raw, like that.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If they caught you eating a potato, you could have been shot on the spot, because it was called sabotage.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So you had to be very careful what you were doing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We carted this with wheelbarrows into this pit.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
